{"type": "article", "id": 3514, "title": "ilomio Cowbelle系列灯饰", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-13T08:06:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232931KzTQZ1elyYfik8nC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦灯饰品牌 ilomio 日前推出了迷你 LED 灯具系列「Cowbelle」，从这一系列灯具的名字不难看出，其造型的设计灵感来源于牛颈铃的外形，又结合了北欧代表性的极简主义风格与现代主义的元素。Cowbelle 系列均由回收的航天级的铝合金材料制作而成，包括有吊灯、台灯以及落地灯，灯罩顶部配有一根小型皮带，便于运输或者携带，提供黑、白、红、灰以及蓝 5 种丰富的色彩选择。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232929FcjbWHfo7d2xM495.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232929EH7gXY5kuyWxlOZP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232929UhxMzF4AS1n8vg3m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232930soNzaSwGMpxWvCPU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232930yEBxkLsUdOpvXaV1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232930e4ZpHBvFxdMJhulY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}